   EXCLUSIVE-MIDEAST-SPY (Washington) _ A behind-the-scenes
examination of high-level discord over the imprisoned spy Jonathan
Pollard during the Wye, Md., Mideast peace talks. By James Risen
and by Steven Erlanger.
</P>
<P>
   CHINA-TIBET (Lhasa, Tibet) _ Tibet, whose people have preserved
a remarkable religious devotion despite decades of persecution by
the Chinese, are now facing the onslaught of China's free-wheeling
economic boom. By Seth Faison. ART ADV: Photo has been sent to NYT
photo clients. Locator map has been sent to NYT graphics clients.)
