<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    Q &AMP; A ON THE NEWS
 &HT;    By Colin Bessonette
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   UNDATED: restricted airspace.
</P>
<P>
   Q: I watched the recent TV miniseries about the singing group
Temptations, and it made me wonder: Who are the people billed as
