added.
</P>
<P>
   Q: Where do astronauts sleep when they're in space? Are they in
a hammock or bed of some type?
</P>
<P>
   A: On the current space shuttle Discovery mission, John Glenn
and the other astronauts sleep in small, rectangular containers,
