<DOCTYPE> NEWS STORY </DOCTYPE>
<DATE_TIME> 1998-11-11 13:42 </DATE_TIME>
<HEADER>
A5107 &Cx1f; tdt-z
u e &Cx13;  &Cx11;  BC-AUTHOR-WOLFE-2TAKES-B     11-11 0982
