(editors: changes `Intranet' to `Internet' in last graph.) &QL; 
New Browsers Offer Excellent Online Security &LR;
</P>
<P>
   &QL; 
 &UR; By David Einstein &QL; 
c.1998 San Francisco Chronicle &QC;  &LR; What's the true status with online
security these days? Is it good enough so I don't have to worry
about giving my credit card number online?
U,A,: - BC-CIR-TEENS-ONLINE-ART-, -  &QL; 
 &UR; BC-CIR-TEENS-ONLINE-ART-2TAKES-NYT &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; (ATTN: Va., Mass., N.Y., Texas) &LR;  &QL; 
 &UR; YAKETY-YAK, CLACKETY-CLACK &LR;  &QL; 
