<P>
   DEFORESTATION-FLOODS (Tegucigalpa, Honduras) -- What seemed a
natural disaster in Central America was, in many ways, a manmade
disaster because of extensive deforestation. And chances are that
rebuilding efforts _ clear-cut logging, riverbank housing _ will
create worse conditions. By David L. Marcus. 1100 words.
</P>
<P>
   HONGKONG-PLA (Hong Kong) -- Contrary to fears of many in Hong
Kong, the People's Liberation Army is keeping a low profile there.
By Indira A.R. Lakshmanan.
</P>
<P>
