<HEADLINE>
&HT;   
</HEADLINE>
 &HT;    DEBATE GEARS UP ON PRIVATE ACCOUNTS FOR SOCIAL SECURITY
 &HT;    Moving in (w) Washington and (f) financial categories.
 &HT;    By JULIA MALONE
 &HT;    c.1998 Cox News Service
