like gym class. For the University of Dayton football team, just to
show up breathing was enough. This year the Flyers are 5-4 and the
point differential is 244-235. To the philospher who said, ``May
you live in interesting times,'' UD coach Mike Kelly says, ``It's
killing me.'' (Nuhn, Dayton Daily News) MOVED.
</P>
