 &HT;    SPOTLIGHT ON . . .KRISTIN SCOTT THOMAS
 &HT;    c. 1998 Cox News Service
<TEXT>
<P>
   (``The Horse Whisperer'')
</P>
<P>
   ``Four Weddings and a Funeral'': Pining for Hugh Grant.
</P>
<P>
   ``Angels &AMP; Insects'': Drabbed down as a governess in this
twisted Victorian fable.
</P>
<P>
   ``Richard III'': Seduced by evil politico Ian McKellen.
</P>
<P>
   ``The English Patient'': Forming a desert triangle with Ralph
Fiennes and Colin Firth.
