 &UR; LEVI _ &LR;  Levi Strauss &AMP; Co. will start selling Levi's and Dockers
clothing over its World Wide Web sites later this month, a move
that may boost sales for the troubled company, but also could
alienate the retailers that sell its wares. By Carol Emert
</P>
