Rep. Steve Largent of Oklahoma and Rep. Jennifer Dunn of
Washington.
</P>
<P>
   Several Republican handicappers said Wednesday that while Armey
might so far have an advantage in commitments for the Nov. 18
secret-ballot election, he had not yet achieved a dominance that
would allow him to claim victory in the initial round of voting.
